data.description: Wow! This property has lots to offer! 1.7 acre property with 21 shares of DeWeese Dye Ditch for irrigation,two houses, and an oversized 1 car detached garage. The main 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom house is ready foryou to do the finishing work exactly as you would like and have a nice home.No permit was pulled on the shed/guest house which includes1 bedroom,living room, kitchen, and bathroom. Needs some updating but livable.Come explore the potential of this unique property.
